def read_queries_and_freq(row):
    key, value = row.split('\t', 1)
    key = ujson.loads(key)
    value = ujson.loads(value)
    city, query = key.split(':', 1)
    
    return T.Row(bow_query=query, city=city, explicit_freq=sum(value['nobow_queries'].values()))
    
    
candidates = sc.textFile('s3://cliqz-data-pipeline/work_area/index_freshness/v1/geolocal/results/20180816/all/').map(read_queries_and_freq).toDF().cache()
candidates.count()

%pyspark
def map_only_queries(row):
    key, value = row.split('\t', 1)
    city, bow_query = key.split(':', 1)
    return T.Row(bow_query=bow_query)

geolocal_queries.count()

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
def process(row):
    total_explicit_freq = float(sum(row.explicit_freqs))
    
    for city, explicit_freq in zip(row.cities, row.explicit_freqs):
        possible_freq = row.freq * explicit_freq / total_explicit_freq
        yield T.Row(
            bow_query=row.bow_query,
            city=city,
            nobow_queries=row.nobow_queries,
            possible_freq=possible_freq,
        )

prepared_dataset = (final_dataset
    .where(final_dataset.city != 'no-city')
    .groupby(final_dataset.bow_query)
    .agg(
        F.collect_list(final_dataset.city).alias('cities'),
        F.collect_list(final_dataset.explicit_freq).alias('explicit_freqs'),
        F.first(final_dataset.nobow_queries).alias('nobow_queries'),
        F.first(final_dataset.freq).alias('freq'),
    )
    .rdd
    .flatMap(process)
    .toDF()
    .sort(F.col('possible_freq').desc())
    .cache())
    
prepared_dataset.count()
